<title>ạ̉nạ ly myn fy ạlʿmr swạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̉nạ ly myn fy ạlʿmr swạk .. gẖyrk ạ̹nt yạ ḍạmn ạ̉yạmy
 rfyq wḥbyb wạ̉gẖly̱ nṣyb .. btdạwy jrạḥy wậlạmy)2
 (ạ̹nt rby mạlk qlby)2
 (mạ ạnt ạlly ḍạmn ạ̉yạmy .. wf ạ̹ydk ʿmry wslạmy)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉nạ lyk ạ̉nạ lyk .. ạ̉nạ lyk yạ ḍạmn ạ̉yạmy)2
 2- (tsbyḥ mn qlby wạ̉gẖạny .. tsẖkr sẖkẖṣk ạlly fdạny
 tʿln mjdk ʿẓmẗ ḥbk .. wḥnạn qlbk ạlly rʿạny)2
 (ạ̹nt ʿzy mjdy wtrsy)2
 (yʿjz lsạny wklạmy .. ʿn wṣf ḥbk ạlsạmy)2
 3- (yṣgẖr ạlʿạlm fy ʿyny .. lmạ bạsẖwf ʿmlk ʿlsẖạny
 ạ̉nsy̱ nfsy kl mạ ʿndy .. ạ̹nt gẖạyty wkl ậmạly)2
 (ạ̹nt ʿạly fwq kl gẖạly)2
 (ạ̹yh ysẖbʿ nfsy wygẖnyny .. gẖyr nẓrẗ ḥbk tkfyny)2</lyrics>
</song>